Pre-processing steps

Marcos Nascimento and Arantxa Cebrian-Silla

library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)

options(future.globals.maxSize = 16 * 1024^3)  # Example: 16 GB

source("../my_functions.R") #Loading a couple of custom functions for plotting

#Batch_1

Loading CellRanger data

Generated using 10xv3 chemistry, published on eLife in 2021

batch1_exp <- readRDS('/media/data5/marcos/publication_objects/elife_2021/scSeq.rds') %>% UpdateSeuratObject()
batch1_cells <- colnames(batch1_exp)
write(batch1_cells, 'data/batch1_cells.txt')

Loading STARsolo data

batch1_g1 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/BMAB01/g1/raw')
batch1_g2 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/BMAB01/g2/raw')
batch1_g2@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0('2_', batch1_g2@Dimnames[[2]])

batch1_starsolo <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = c(batch1_g1, batch1_g2)) %>% subset(cells = batch1_cells)
batch1_starsolo <- JoinLayers(batch1_starsolo)
saveRDS(batch1_starsolo, 'batch1_starsolo.rds', compress = F)

#Batch_2 ## Loading CellRanger data

batch2_exp <- readRDS('/media/data5/arantxa/ACSAAB01/pre-processing/3.batch_correction/exp.step3.rds')

p365_cells <- batch2_exp@meta.data %>% filter(region == 'Old LW') %>% rownames()

batch2_exp@meta.data[p365_cells, 'region'] <- 'LW'
batch2_exp@meta.data[, 'age'] <- 'p30'
batch2_exp@meta.data[p365_cells, 'age'] <- 'p365'

batch2_exp$region %>% unique()
#batch2_cells <- colnames(batch2_exp) #previous version
batch2_cells <- batch2_exp@meta.data %>% filter(age == 'p30' & 
                                                region %in% c('LW', 'Wedge')) %>% 
                  rownames()

write(batch2_cells, 'data/batch2_cells.txt')
write(p365_cells, 'data/p365_cells.txt')

Loading STARsolo data

batch2_g1 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB01/g1/raw')
batch2_g2 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB01/g2/raw')
batch2_g1@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch2_g1@Dimnames[[2]], '-1')
batch2_g2@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch2_g2@Dimnames[[2]], '-2')

batch2_starsolo <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = c(batch2_g1, batch2_g2)) %>% subset(cells = batch2_cells)
batch2_starsolo <- JoinLayers(batch2_starsolo)

#Adding P365------------
batch2_starsolo_withp365 <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = c(batch2_g1, batch2_g2)) %>% subset(cells = c(batch2_cells, p365_cells))
batch2_starsolo_withp365 <- JoinLayers(batch2_starsolo_withp365)

#saveRDS(batch2_starsolo, 'batch2_starsolo.rds', compress = F)
saveRDS(batch2_starsolo_withp365, 'batch2_starsolo_withp365.rds', compress = F)

#Batch_3 ## Loading CellRanger data

batch3_exp <- readRDS('/media/data5/arantxa/ACSAAB02/exp.combined.100dims.rds')
batch3_exp$sample %>% unique() #only LW and Wedge at P30 and P9 in this dataset

#batch3_cells <- colnames(batch3_exp) # previous version
batch3_cells <- batch3_exp@meta.data %>% filter(age == 'P30') %>% rownames()
p9_cells <- batch3_exp@meta.data %>% filter(age == 'P9') %>% rownames()


write(batch3_cells, 'data/batch3_cells.txt')
write(p9_cells, 'data/p9_cells.txt')

Loading STARsolo data

batch3_g1 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB02/g1/raw')
batch3_g2 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB02/g2/raw')
batch3_g3 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB02/g3/raw')
batch3_g4 <- ReadSTARsolo('/media/data1/marcos/b2/inputs/ACSAAB02/g4/raw')

batch3_g1@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch3_g1@Dimnames[[2]], '-1_1')
batch3_g2@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch3_g2@Dimnames[[2]], '-1_2')
batch3_g3@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch3_g3@Dimnames[[2]], '-1_3')
batch3_g4@Dimnames[[2]] <- paste0(batch3_g4@Dimnames[[2]], '-1_4')

batch3_starsolo <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = c(batch3_g1, batch3_g2, batch3_g3, batch3_g4)) %>% subset(cells = batch3_cells)
batch3_starsolo <- JoinLayers(batch3_starsolo)

saveRDS(batch3_starsolo, 'batch3_starsolo.rds', compress = F)

#Adding P9------------
batch3_starsolo_withp9 <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = c(batch3_g1, batch3_g2, batch3_g3, batch3_g4)) %>% subset(cells = c(batch3_cells, p9_cells))
batch3_starsolo_withp9 <- JoinLayers(batch3_starsolo_withp9)

saveRDS(batch3_starsolo_withp9, 'batch3_starsolo_withp9.rds', compress = F)
ncol(batch1_starsolo) == ncol(batch1_exp)
ncol(batch2_starsolo) == ncol(batch2_exp)
ncol(batch3_starsolo) == ncol(batch3_exp)

Integration

Merging datasets

#objects <- list(batch1_starsolo, batch2_starsolo, batch3_starsolo) #previous version
objects <- list(batch1_starsolo, batch2_starsolo_withp365, batch3_starsolo_withp9)
integrated_exp <- merge(objects[[1]], objects[-1])

Merging metadata

batch1_metadata <- batch1_exp@meta.data
batch2_metadata <- batch2_exp@meta.data[c(batch2_cells, p365_cells), ]
batch3_metadata <- batch3_exp@meta.data[c(batch3_cells, p9_cells), ]

batch1_metadata <- batch1_metadata %>% 
                    dplyr::select('cell_type_batch1' = 'Cell_Type', 'sublibrary' = 'Lane') %>% 
                    mutate(batch = 'batch_1',
                           region = 'LV',
                           age = 'p30', 
                           sample = paste(age, region, sep = '_'))

batch2_metadata <- batch2_metadata %>%
                   dplyr::select('sublibrary' = 'well', 'region', 'age') %>%
                   mutate(batch = 'batch_2',
                          sample = paste(age, region, sep = '_'))

batch3_metadata <- batch3_metadata %>% 
                   dplyr::select('age', 'sample', 'region',  'sublibrary' = 'well') %>% 
                   mutate(batch = 'batch_3')

all_meta <- bind_rows(batch1_metadata, batch2_metadata, batch3_metadata)
all_meta$batch %>% table()
integrated_exp@meta.data <- left_join(integrated_exp@meta.data %>% rownames_to_column('rn'), 
                              all_meta %>%
                                rownames_to_column('rn'), 
                              by = 'rn') %>% 
  column_to_rownames('rn')

integrated_exp$age <- integrated_exp$age %>% gsub('^P', 'p', .) 

integrated_exp[['percent.mt']] <- PercentageFeatureSet(integrated_exp, pattern = '^mt-')

integrated_exp@meta.data 
integrated_exp$age %>% unique()
integrated_exp$region %>% unique()
# integrated_exp <- integrated_exp %>%
#   subset(cells = cells_to_use) 

integrated_exp <- integrated_exp %>% 
  SCTransform() %>% 
  RunPCA(npcs = 100) %>% 
  RunUMAP(dims = 1:100, 
          reduction = 'pca',
          reduction.name = 'nonint')

Integrating

integrated_exp <- IntegrateLayers(integrated_exp, 
                                  method = CCAIntegration, 
                                  normalization.method = 'SCT') %>% 
                    RunUMAP(dims = 1:100, 
                            reduction = 'integrated.dr') %>% 
                    FindNeighbors(dims = 1:100, 
                                  reduction = 'integrated.dr') %>%
                    FindClusters(resolution = seq(0.5, 2, 0.5))
(mDimPlot(integrated_exp, group.by = 'batch', shuffle = T) + 
  labs(title = 'Integrated UMAP')) +
(mDimPlot(integrated_exp, group.by = 'batch', shuffle = T, reduction = 'nonint') + 
  labs(title = 'Non-integrated UMAP'))


(mDimPlot(integrated_exp, group.by = 'age', shuffle = T) + 
  labs(title = 'Integrated UMAP')) +
(mDimPlot(integrated_exp, group.by = 'age', shuffle = T, reduction = 'nonint') + 
  labs(title = 'Non-integrated UMAP'))

mDimPlot(integrated_exp, shuffle = T, group.by = 'cell_type_batch1', label = T)

mDimPlot(integrated_exp, shuffle = T, group.by = c('batch', 'region', 'age'), ncol = 3) 


mFeaturePlot(integrated_exp, features = c('Thbs4', 'Adamts18', 'Hgf', 'Igsf21', 'Notum', 'Bmper', 'Crym', 'Npy'), order = F, ncol = 4, legend = F)

Cell type annotation

P30+P365


Idents(integrated_exp) = 'SCT_snn_res.2'

integrated_exp@meta.data <- integrated_exp@meta.data %>%
  mutate(cell_type = case_when(
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(33, 11, 0, 43, 35) ~ 'Ependymal cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(22, 28) ~ 'Astrocytes',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(16, 8, 18, 26, 20) ~ 'B cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 == 10 ~ 'C cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(12, 9, 17, 24) ~ 'Dividing cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(29, 15, 4, 46, 23, 14, 1, 30, 21, 7, 5, 6) ~ 'A cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 == 44 ~ 'VLMC',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(13, 45, 19) ~ 'OPC',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(36, 32) ~ 'Oligodendrocytes',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(31, 3, 42) ~ 'Microglia',
    SCT_snn_res.2 == 37 ~ 'Myeloid cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(2, 41, 27) ~ 'Endothelial cells',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(25, 40) ~ 'Pericytes/VSMC',
    SCT_snn_res.2 %in% c(38, 39, 34) ~ 'Neurons',
    TRUE ~ 'Unknown'
  ))


DimPlot(integrated_exp, 
        group.by = 'cell_type', 
        label=T, 
        cols = c('indianred2','plum3','steelblue3', 'seagreen3', 'gold','pink', 'sandybrown','hotpink', 'grey','brown3','brown', 'maroon3','magenta4','coral','pink')) +
  NoLegend() + 
  coord_fixed() + 
  NoAxes()



DimPlot(integrated_exp, 
        group.by = 'cell_type', 
        label=F, 
        cols = c('indianred2','grey','steelblue3', 'seagreen3', 'gold','grey', 'grey','grey', 'grey','grey','grey', 'grey','grey','grey','grey')) +
  NoLegend() + 
  coord_fixed() + 
  NoAxes()


DimPlot(integrated_exp, 
        group.by = 'cell_type', 
        label=FALSE, 
        cols = c('grey', 'grey','steelblue3', 'grey', 'grey', 'grey','grey','grey', 'grey','grey', 'grey', 'grey', 'grey', 'grey')) + 
  NoLegend() + 
  coord_fixed() + 
  NoAxes()
